""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[BrowserId], [c].[Finished], [c].[InsertTime], [c].[IsRemoved], [c].[RemoveTime], [c].[UpdateTime], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE ([c].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND (([c].[BrowserId] = @__BrowserId_0) AND ([c].[Finished] <> CAST(1 AS bit)))
    ORDER BY [c].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]

) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[BrowserId], [c].[Finished], [c].[InsertTime], [c].[IsRemoved], [c].[RemoveTime], [c].[UpdateTime], [c].[UserId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[BrowserId], [c].[Finished], [c].[InsertTime], [c].[IsRemoved], [c].[RemoveTime], [c].[UpdateTime], [c].[UserId]

) AS [t]

    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[BrowserId], [c].[Finished], [c].[InsertTime], [c].[IsRemoved], [c].[RemoveTime], [c].[UpdateTime], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE ([c].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND (([c].[BrowserId] = @__BrowserId_0) AND ([c].[Finished] <> CAST(1 AS bit)))
    ORDER BY [c].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[BrowserId], [c].[Finished], [c].[InsertTime], [c].[IsRemoved], [c].[RemoveTime], [c].[UpdateTime], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]

    WHERE ([c].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND (([c].[BrowserId] = @__BrowserId_0) AND ([c].[Finished] <> CAST(1 AS bit)))
    ORDER BY [c].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[BrowserId], [c].[Finished], [c].[InsertTime], [c].[IsRemoved], [c].[RemoveTime], [c].[UpdateTime], [c].[UserId]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]

        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[Count], [c0].[InsertTime], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[Price], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[RemoveTime], [c0].[UpdateTime], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [p].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [p].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [p].[UserId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

) AS [t]

    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE [c0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
